quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif. Lam. Ra. Tsena ke litemana tsa Qura’n, – tseo eleng manollo e hlakileng"
  15,2,"Mahana-tumelo a tla tlaloa ke takatso ea hore ba ke beba ile ba inamela thatong ea Allah, Islamong"
  15,3,"Ba tloheleng ba je le hona ho natefeloa le ho ithabisa. Ha Ts’epo ea bohata e ba thabise: Haufi ba tla ruoa tsebo"
  15,4,Ha Re’a ka Ra timetsa sechaba empa ho sa ka ha eba le pallo malebana le ona
  15,5,"Etsoe ho se sechaba se ka itlhophelang nako eo ea pallo, kapa hona hore ba e liehise"
  15,6,"Ba re: “Hela uena eo molaetsa o senotsoeng ho uena, Ruri u’a hlanya"
  15,7,"Hobaneng u sa tlise manyeloi ho rona, haeba u le e mong oa ba nang le ‘Nete?”"
  15,8,"Ha Re ke Re romela manyeloi haese feela ka lebaka le tiileng, ha ane a ka tla, Bonang! ba ne ba tla hloka phomolo"
  15,9,Re theoletse Molaetsa ona kantle ho qeaqeo; Ruri Re balebeli ba oona
  15,10,Re romeletse Baromuoa pele ho uena har’a batho ba litumelo tsa khale
  15,11,Ha ho le’a mong oa baromuoa eo ba sa kang ba mo soma
  15,12,Ke kamoo re etsang hore e kene lipelong tsa ba molato
  15,13,"Hore ha ba kholoe ho oona, le hoja mohlala oa batho ba khale o se o fetile pele"
  15,14,"Le haeba Re ne Re ba buletse khoro ea leholimo, bane ba tla qeta letsatsi lohle ho nyolohela teng"
  15,15,"Ba re: “Mahlo a rona a tahiloe: che, re mpa re loiloe.”"
  15,16,"Ke Rona ba thalehileng maholimo ka Mats’oao a Linaleli, Ra le ntlafatsa sebakeng sa babohi"
  15,17,Re A ts’irelelitse malebana le meea eohle ea liabolosi e lits’ila
  15,18,"Empa ea fumanang kutlo ka bokhukhuni, o salangoe ke khanare ea lelakabe"
  15,19,"Haele lefats’e lona re le alile joaloka moseme, eaba re beha holim’a lona Lithaba tse tsepameng ka tieo; le hona ho hlahisa lintho tsohle tsa mefuta holim’a lona ka tekano"
  15,20,Re le nehile boipheliso holim’a lona ekasitana le bao uena o sa ba fepeng letho
  15,21,Ha ho letho le teng leo mehloli ea lona e seng ho Rona. Ha Re romelle letho lefats’eng haese ka tekanyo e lekaneng
  15,22,"Re bile Re romella liphefo tse matlafatsang, le hona ho nesa pula e tsoang marung ho le neha metsi. Empa le se balebeli ba mehloli eo"
  15,23,"Ruri! Ke Rona ba fanang ka bophelo, le ho fana ka lefu, ke Rona ba salang E le majalefa"
  15,24,Ruri Re’a tseba ka ba potlakelang pele har’a lona le ba le le sisitheho
  15,25,"Bona! Mong`a hau U tla ba khobokanya ‘moho. Hobane Ruri U Seli, U hlokolosi"
  15,26,"Re hlotse motho ka letsopa le lets’o, le tsoang seretseng se khobiloeng la nehoa sebopeho"
  15,27,Pele re hlotse Masabonoeng ka mollo o tlotlehang
  15,28,"U be u hopole mohla Mong`a hau A neng A re ho manyeloi: “bonang! Ke morerong oa ho hlola motho ka letsopa le lets’o le tsoang seretseng le tla nehoa sebopeho"
  15,29,"Ho ba ke mo hlole le hona ho bolulela moea oa ka U halalelang ka ho eena, le oele fats’e ka boikokobetso kapela hae.”"
  15,30,Manyeloi ohle a ile a ithapalatsa ka boikokobetso ‘moho
  15,31,Haese Iblis. Ea ileng a hana hoba har’a ba ithapalatsang
  15,32,"Allah A re: “Oho Iblis! Ke lefeng lebaka le entseng hore u se ke oa ba har’a ba ithapalatsang?”"
  15,33,"Iblis a re: “Nka ithapalatsa joang ho motho eo u mo hlotseng ka letsopa le lets’o le tsoang seretseng, eaba le’a khojoa le nehoa sebopeho?”"
  15,34,"Allah A re: “Tloha mona ke hona, hobane o ea khesehang"
  15,35,Thohako e tlaba holim’a hau ho fihlela Letsatsi la Kahlolo.”
  15,36,"Iblis a re: “Mong`a ka! A k’u mphe nyehlisetso ho fihlela Letsatsi leo ba tlang ho tsosoa ka lona.”"
  15,37,"Allah A re: “Nyehlisetso o e filoe"
  15,38,Ho fihlela Nako ea Pallo.”
  15,39,"Iblis a re: “Mong`a ka! Ho latela hore u ntahletse thoko le tsela e nepahetseng, Ruri ke tla ntlafatsa tsela e fosahetseng malebana le batho ba lefats’eng, ke tla khelosa bohle tseleng e nepahetseng"
  15,40,Ntle le makhabunyane a hau a ts’epahalang a bileng a hloekisitsoeng.”
  15,41,"Allah A re: “Ena ke tsela e nepahetseng ea makhabunyane a ka, ebile e le setlamo ho ‘na"
  15,42,"Haele makhabunyane ha u ope o tlang ho ba le matla holim’a hae, ntle le ba ikenyang phosong ba o latele"
  15,43,Ruri lihele ke sebaka seo ba se t`sepisitsoeng
  15,44,"Se na le likhoro tse supileng, khoro ka `ngoe e na le karolo ea eona ea pallo"
  15,45,Ba lokileng ba tla ba har’a lirapa le liliba
  15,46,"Ho tla thoe ho bona: “Kenang ho tsona ka Khotso le Paballeho.”"
  15,47,Re tla hlakola eng kapa eng ekabang teng e mpe ka hare ho lifuba tsa bona. E tla ba baena ba tla beng ba lutse litulong tse phahameng ba shebane ka mahlong
  15,48,"Ho se khathatso ea letho e ka ba t`soenyang moo, kapa hona ho lelekoa sebakeng seo.”"
  15,49,"Bolella makhabunyane A ka hore, Ruri Ke Ts’oarela-joalo- joalo, ebile Ke Khaphatseha Mohau"